nticipation\", \"from\": 367, \"to\": 379}, {\"ngram\": \"the bell\", \"from\": 383, \"to\": 391}, {\"ngram\": \"being rung\", \"from\": 392, \"to\": 402}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But after watchingSweden's Armand Duplantis ring the bell following his successful world record attempt in the men's pole vault on Monday evening, Logan shared her theory about the Olympic bell not being completely genuine.\", \"from\": 405, \"to\": 628, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 432, \"end\": 448, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Armand_Duplantis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Armand Duplantis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Armand_Duplantis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Armand_Duplantis\"}, {\"begin\": 552, \"end\": 557, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Logan_River\", \"score\": 0.5871630656256223, \"rank\": 0.7030574872372262, \"text\": \"Logan\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Logan_River\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Logan_River\"}, {\"begin\": 586, \"end\": 598, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Bell\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Olympic bell\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Bell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Bell\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the bell\", \"from\": 454, \"to\": 462}, {\"ngram\": \"his successful world record attempt\", \"from\": 473, \"to\": 508}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's pole vault\", \"from\": 512, \"to\": 532}, {\"ngram\": \"Monday evening\", \"from\": 536, \"to\": 550}, {\"ngram\": \"her theory\", \"from\": 565, \"to\": 575}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Now, I have noticed this that the bell starts to ring before the athlete actually pulls the bell,' Logan said.\", \"from\": 630, \"to\": 741, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 730, \"end\": 735, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Logan_River\", \"score\": 0.5871630656256223, \"rank\": 0.7030574872372262, \"text\": \"Logan\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Logan_River\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Logan_River\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the bell\", \"from\": 661, \"to\": 669}, {\"ngram\": \"the athlete\", \"from\": 692, \"to\": 703}, {\"ngram\": \"the bell\", \"from\": 719, \"to\": 727}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'So, I am hoping I am not seeing\\u2026 it's like Santa Claus, is that what I am seeing is real?'\", \"from\": 743, \"to\": 834, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 787, \"end\": 798, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Santa_Claus\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 2.0883160161710972e-13, \"text\": \"Santa Claus\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Santa_Claus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Santa_Claus\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Former United States sprinter Michael Johnson, who is working as a pundit for the BBC in Paris, replied: 'I think it's a little delay on our monitor.\", \"from\": 836, \"to\": 985, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 843, \"end\": 856, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999686885928387, \"rank\": 2.113495181354814e-05, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 866, \"end\": 881, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Johnson_(sprinter)\", \"score\": 0.6562406956374156, \"rank\": 0.27532889874352734, \"text\": \"Michael Johnson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Johnson_(sprinter)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Johnson_(sprinter)\"}, {\"begin\": 918, \"end\": 921, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"score\": 0.9988276789965927, \"rank\": 0.0011520244734597922, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\"}, {\"begin\": 925, \"end\": 930, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999938609, \"rank\": 6.149270795665201e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a pundit\", \"from\": 901, \"to\": 909}, {\"ngram\": \"a little delay\", \"from\": 955, \"to\": 969}, {\"ngram\": \"our monitor\", \"from\": 973, \"to\": 984}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think that's what it is.'\", \"from\": 986, \"to\": 1013, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Logan then said: 'Is there a little bit of theatre going on down there?\", \"from\": 1015, \"to\": 1086, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1015, \"end\": 1020, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Logan_River\", \"score\": 0.5871630656256223, \"rank\": 0.7030574872372262, \"text\": \"Logan\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Logan_River\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Logan_River\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a little bit\", \"from\": 1042, \"to\": 1054}, {\"ngram\": \"theatre\", \"from\": 1058, \"to\": 1065}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Okay, alright.'\", \"from\": 1087, \"to\": 1102, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Johnson jokingly replied: 'You just want to go down there and do it.'\", \"from\": 1104, \"to\": 1173, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1104, \"end\": 1111, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyndon_B._Johnson\", \"score\": 0.8952157887014643, \"rank\": 0.11509608711914501, \"text\": \"Johnson\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyndon_B._Johnson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyndon_B._Johnson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Logan then finished by saying: 'Well, in the name of good journalism, I want to make sure that bell is real.\", \"from\": 1175, \"to\": 1283, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1175, \"end\": 1180, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Logan_River\", \"score\": 0.5871630656256223, \"rank\": 0.7030574872372262, \"text\": \"Logan\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Logan_River\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Logan_River\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the name\", \"from\": 1216, \"to\": 1224}, {\"ngram\": \"good journalism\", \"from\": 1228, \"to\": 1243}, {\"ngram\": \"bell\", \"from\": 1270, \"to\": 1274}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We will be investigating that and maybe send you down Michael to ring the bell.'\", \"from\": 1284, \"to\": 1364, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Michael\", \"from\": 1338, \"to\": 1345}, {\"ngram\": \"the bell\", \"from\": 1354, \"to\": 1362}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Johnson's explanation may be the most credible explanation to Logan's theory as the bell was tested by United States sprinting legend Carl Lewis on Thursday alongside Paris 2024 chief organiser Tony Estanguet.\", \"from\": 1366, \"to\": 1575, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1366, \"end\": 1373, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyndon_B._Johnson\", \"score\": 0.8952157887014643, \"rank\": 0.11509608711914501, \"text\": \"Johnson\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyndon_B._Johnson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyndon_B._Johnson\"}, {\"begin\": 1428, \"end\": 1433, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Logan_River\", \"score\": 0.5871630656256223, \"rank\": 0.7030574872372262, \"text\": \"Logan\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Logan_River\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Logan_River\"}, {\"begin\": 1469, \"end\": 1482, \"